%% Upload Status State Machine
%% Tracks file upload lifecycle from submission to completion

stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> pending : POST /api/uploads

    pending --> processing : Format detected,\nsingle-sheet file
    pending --> awaiting_input : Multi-sheet file\ndetected

    awaiting_input --> processing : POST /api/uploads/{id}/process\n(user selects sheet)

    processing --> completed : Parquet conversion +\ndataset creation success
    processing --> failed : Conversion error or\nstorage failure

    completed --> [*]
    failed --> [*]

    state pending {
        [*] --> raw_stored : File saved to MinIO
        raw_stored --> format_detected : Plugin identifies format
    }

    state processing {
        [*] --> converting : Parquet conversion
        converting --> partitioning : Apply partition fields
        partitioning --> storing : Upload to S3
        storing --> profiling : Generate previews +\ncolumn profiles
        profiling --> creating : Create Dataset record
    }

    note right of awaiting_input
        Response includes:
        - choices: available sheets
        - preview_rows: sample data
    end note

    note right of completed
        Response includes:
        - dataset_id (or dataset_ids)
        - converted_storage_path
        - preview_rows
    end note
